{"tid":2515983,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"港台網站無法從海外登入  網站：It works","createTime":"2021-05-04T10:44:16.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-04T10:46:00.000Z","uid":305269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"8cc99c15b9ff3e4ef1ae8be9eb934652c918fbb2","tid":2515983,"uid":305269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T10:44:16.000Z","msg":"香港電台網站下午一度未能從海外登入。下午一時許，有在美國和澳洲的用戶表示，登入本台網站後，出現白色畫面，左上角顯示「It works!」的細字，直至下午較後時間恢復正常。在本港，網站能如常登入。<br />\n<br />\n港台發言人回覆查詢時表示，港台其中一組伺服器出現短暫及局部故障，因此曾影響一些用戶進入港台網站，經工程人員維修，服務回復正常。<br />\n<br />\n#RTHK #香港電台<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/715486135226112/posts/4517438848364136/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F715486135226112%2Fposts%2F4517438848364136%2F&d=4vQCcaBbFH%2F4J6PBkjxGnmzUwbN2nhMFbUYjFdDHJd4%3D&h=e4e6c32b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/715486135226112/posts/4517438848364136/</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmQ4WATAj6rpb8UQmhkELwK5uz88798BfqjvkQ2eWpbMi1?filename=ZfKXCPD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZfKXCPD.jpg&h=2710be00&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n港台網站：<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmYqMKmGvbg4LMXrmVcuRgFsS1PTvTqbXW8PA78dzVgSjo?filename=XZdUE3X.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXZdUE3X.jpg&h=b968ceb5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"560cf98299a954a99a539cdd41ff0897946f1bcc","tid":2515983,"uid":36178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T10:45:15.000Z","msg":"It works<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e86e49c1fd42917a868ee1e3b3b1aea01578c687","tid":2515983,"uid":305269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"560cf98299a954a99a539cdd41ff0897946f1bcc","tid":2515983,"uid":36178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T10:45:15.000Z","msg":"It works<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal